    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔力构造》是一款<strong>自由编辑技能</strong>的动作生存类游戏。在这里，你将通过一次次升级和命运的抉择，打造独一无二的角色成长路径。利用<strong>简单的连接机制</strong>，自由组合技能模块，构筑属于你的专属技能，在充满挑战的世界中生存并变强。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次冒险都是全新的体验，每一次选择都将改变你的命运。你，准备好迎接这场魔法与生存的终极挑战了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>战斗系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >临危不乱的战斗体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爽快附带异常状态的攻击</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各种各样的神奇怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/7d46f3097cf591123ac2c42eed4e90e6.poster.avif?t=1748414538\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/7d46f3097cf591123ac2c42eed4e90e6.webm?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/7d46f3097cf591123ac2c42eed4e90e6.mp4?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/f8f1d5d84738688d014c039cfd05feb8.poster.avif?t=1748414538\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/f8f1d5d84738688d014c039cfd05feb8.webm?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/f8f1d5d84738688d014c039cfd05feb8.mp4?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/d6ce5d710672461480f3464bc95063e6.poster.avif?t=1748414538\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/d6ce5d710672461480f3464bc95063e6.webm?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/d6ce5d710672461480f3464bc95063e6.mp4?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>技能系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过连接新的插件，使投射物获得此插件的属性</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >连接的插件越多，投射物也就越强</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分插件的属性可以调节</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/0de9c0098b64bc599c0c06d2f79d2495.poster.avif?t=1748414538\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/0de9c0098b64bc599c0c06d2f79d2495.webm?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/0de9c0098b64bc599c0c06d2f79d2495.mp4?t=1748414538\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>难度系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个地图都提供了多种多样的标签</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每种标签对应一种机制</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过选择各个标签实现不一样的游戏体验</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/c7b82795c700c632b56bc6100f5a7509.avif?t=1748414538\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras_big/c7b82795c700c632b56bc6100f5a7509.avif?t=1748414538 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>成就系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >解锁成就可获得新的道具、角色、属性等内容</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras/174d28842ad302a81a4e0997f1456274.avif?t=1748414538\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3309810/extras_big/174d28842ad302a81a4e0997f1456274.avif?t=1748414538 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
